I"­œ<p>Some of these resources might be helpful during your time in academia. I have also added some software and GitHub repositories I use daily.
(Most related to academia are taken from <a href="https://clemense.github.io/">Clemens Eppner's webpage</a> and <a href="http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~pliang/">Paul Liang</a>â€™s GitHub)</p>

