      <li>Kate Saenko: <a href="https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1PZj0Sev2yjDu9NNr96S_wwjKCgIDhGmLjW1vtQpDhlk/edit#slide=id.p">How to Write the Introduction for a Research Paper</a></li>
